So as everyone knows, we
had an outage or an issue

00:45:29.560 --> 00:45:31.609
with an attack on
the East Coast,

00:45:31.609 --> 00:45:32.900
and it's right during an event.

00:45:32.900 --> 00:45:35.170
And when you're
doing live events,

00:45:35.170 --> 00:45:36.775
you are feeling it
for the players.

00:45:36.775 --> 00:45:39.150
